snippet.title: 00 Dilly Releasetrailer EN
snippet.description: Experience the adventures of 00 Dilly! The ultimate crash test dummy comes to life! Help Dilly show off his skills while shooting him across the Grand Canyon with strange devices. Collect points, find treasure and soar upward to the highest scores with Dilly!
